    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underquest</strong> 是一款幻想类 角色扮演 冒险游戏，具有快节奏的战斗和深度的库存管理。收集物品并将它们合并为特殊技能。探索随机生成的地牢，体验各种游戏遭遇。通过装备和修饰符升级你的英雄，以创建多样化和强大的构建。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/8ce42c8433f28776e5a51267a88f233e.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >整理不断补充的库存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/199b85845cfe93688d1a2828ad098ced.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >库存将不断补充，所以请快速拆解。将物品相互结合，在战斗中使用获得的能力，或为你的英雄装备盔甲。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >帮助酒馆中的角色并提升自己</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.poster.avif?t=1755107963\" width=616 height=294 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.webm?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265420/extras/389b31b0edc7ce2d4fb61620d746b3fb.mp4?t=1755107963\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的任务之间，你可以在地下酒馆遇到其他角色。了解每个角色的故事，他们会奖励你特殊的好处。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >库存中物品和技能的多种组合 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3个具有独特策略的首领，各种敌人和游戏事件 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >酒馆中的5个角色，各自有自己的故事和升级优势 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地下氏族的冒险故事和封闭地表的神秘</p></li></ul>",
